<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
  </head>
  <body>
    <h5><%= @user.first_name %>,</h5>

    <div class="center-align">
      <div class="row">
        <p>
          Your product <%= @product.title %> on BlueBird.club has expired and you finished
          your sale with $<%= @product.current_sales %> in sales, missing your goal of
          $<%= @product.goal %>.
        </p>
        <h6>
          At this point you have two choices:
        </h6>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="localhost:3000/users?redirect=/needs_attention">Expire the product, receive no sales</a></li>
          <li><a href="localhost:3000/uesrs?redirect=/needs_attention">Grant the discount of $<%= @product.discount %>, and receive $<%= @product.current_sales %> in sales</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <p>
          If you need any help with the process, don't hesitate to reach out to us.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        Your friends, <br>
        BlueBird.club
      </div>
    </div>


  </body>
</html>
